PDL-Probability

PDL probability distribution samplers and density, cumulative distribution, and
quantile functions.  Includes comprehensive PDL to the GNU Scientific Library
(GSL) Random Distribution (randist) functions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

    perldoc PDL::Probability::GSL
    perldoc PDL::Probability::RLike

